.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, spanish, mexican, italian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, biathlon, ice-hockey, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, trike, subway, tram
1. the italian is the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the mexican is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
7. the spanish is on the far right##1
8. the mexican is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | thai   | italian   | mexican | spanish |
| Sport         | biathlon      | tennis | weightlifting      | ice-hockey |
| Transport     | trike | snowmobile        | tram       | subway  |

