.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, nectarine, raspberry, eggplant
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, dancing, singing, chess
4 different pets are kept: pony, turtle, rabbit, frog
1. the person eating nectarine is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the owner of the pony is the person eating nectarine##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
6. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
7. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | raspberry   | eggplant      | nectarine       | lettuce |
| Hobby   | writing | chess | singing     | dancing |
| Pet     | frog     | turtle  | pony | rabbit |

