.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, coffee, juice, iced-tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, drama, family
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, cat, bird, rabbit
1. the owner of the bird is the person watching action movies##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the person watching family movies and the owner of the hedgehog##2
3. the person watching family movies is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
5. the person drinking water is in an even position##4
6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
7. the person watching action movies is the person drinking water##1
8. the owner of the bird is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | juice   | iced-tea          | coffee | water        |
| Movie-Genre   | drama     | crime | family   | action     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | cat         | rabbit         | bird |

