.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, skydiving, dancing, puzzles
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, coach, analyst, writer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, hip-hop, d&b, reggae
1. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
2. the analyst is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the writer is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is between the photographer and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
6. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the analyst##3
7. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is dancing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | board-games      | dancing       | puzzles    |
| Job           | coach  | analyst  | writer | photographer |
| Music-Genre   | reggae      | d&b | hip-hop         | dubstep    |

