.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, tea, mirinda
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, engineer, police-officer, accountant
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, baseball, cycling, biathlon
1. the doctor is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the doctor##3
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the doctor##3
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the doctor##1
7. the doctor is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
8. the engineer is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
9. the accountant is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | cola         | milk  | tea     | mirinda         |
| Job        | accountant | engineer | doctor | police-officer         |
| Sport      | baseball         | cycling  | snowboarding   | biathlon |

