.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, r&b, pop, classical
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, chinese, italian, thai
4 different pets are kept: snake, hedgehog, cat, frog
 1. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
 2. the polish is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 4. the italian is between the fan of r&b and the fan of folk##2
 5. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
 6. the owner of the frog is the fan of pop##1
 7. the thai is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
 9. the chinese is between the fan of classical and the fan of pop##2
10. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | folk  | pop    | r&b | classical    |
| Nationality   | polish | italian | chinese  | thai |
| Pet           | cat   | frog    | snake        | hedgehog   |

