.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, sprite, iced-tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, dressmaker, engineer, paramedic
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, turkish, american, chinese
1. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
2. the dressmaker is on the left of the lawyer##1
3. the chinese is on the left or right of the engineer##3
4. the dressmaker is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the lawyer##1
6. the chinese is on the right of the dressmaker##1
7. the turkish is on the left of the dressmaker##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the turkish##3
9. the person drinking cola is on the left of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | cola                | iced-tea  | mirinda | sprite   |
| Job           | paramedic | dressmaker | lawyer   | engineer |
| Nationality   | turkish         | malaysian     | chinese     | american |

