.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, carrot, radish, zucchini
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, superhero, martial-arts, disaster
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, punk, house, hip-hop
1. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person eating radish is on the far left##1
3. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
4. the person eating radish is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the fan of electronic is between the person watching disaster movies and the fan of hip-hop##2
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating lettuce is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | radish    | carrot  | zucchini  | lettuce |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | superhero | crime | martial-arts |
| Music-Genre   | house    | electronic     | hip-hop    | punk |

