.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, water
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, thai, italian, russian
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, fish, mouse
1. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person drinking soy-milk and the chinese##2
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
3. the italian is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the thai##1
5. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
7. the chinese is on the left or right of the russian##3
8. the italian is the person drinking mirinda##1
9. the russian is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the cat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | soy-milk      | hot-chocolate  | water    |
| Nationality   | italian   | thai | russian | chinese |
| Pet           | mouse      | fish       | chinchilla   | cat      |

