.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, woodworking, rock-climbing, video-games
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, pakistani, canadian, polish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, basketball, cricket, parkour
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the polish is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the chinese##2
7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
8. the pakistani is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting    | rock-climbing | woodworking  | video-games  |
| Nationality   | canadian | pakistani       | polish | chinese |
| Sport         | cricket   | volleyball      | parkour | basketball       |

