.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, juice, soy-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, adventure, musical, action
4 different pets are kept: goat, horse, goldfish, chinchilla
1. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the horse is the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the person drinking juice is the person watching action movies##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is the owner of the horse##1
7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | juice      | mirinda | hot-chocolate     | soy-milk    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | scientific      | adventure | musical |
| Pet           | goldfish   | horse  | goat     | chinchilla |

