.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, lemonade, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, tennis, biathlon, snowboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, skateboard, scooter, roller
1. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person who's sport is rowing is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person driving the skateboard and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
6. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
8. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | lemonade    | iced-tea     | water    | almond-milk        |
| Sport       | biathlon   | rowing | tennis | snowboarding |
| Transport   | roller | scooter      | skateboard    | jet-ski   |

