3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
4. the person eating pepper is on the far left or far right##3
5. the indian is on the left of the malaysian##1
6. the person eating pepper is in an odd position##4
7. the american is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating peas is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | pepper | peas  | spinach   | cauliflower    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | crime     | mystery | romance |
| Nationality   | american   | brazilian | indian | malaysian   |

