4. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the person watching family movies is the indian##1
6. the fan of salsa is on the right of the turkish##1
7. the turkish is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
8. the fan of pop is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | time-travel | family | drama   |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | dubstep   | salsa     | soul    |
| Nationality   | thai  | turkish | indian  | german |

