.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, cucumber, pineapple, zucchini
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, cooking, magic-tricks, drawing
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake, goat
1. the person eating potato is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
4. the person eating pineapple is on the far left##1
5. the person eating cucumber is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person eating potato##1
8. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | pineapple    | cucumber    | potato  | zucchini |
| Hobby   | drawing | cooking | chess | magic-tricks      |
| Pet     | goldfish   | chinchilla        | goat   | snake       |

 